data.description: *** NEW IMPROVED PRICE!!! *** Beautiful rocking chair front porch!   EXCELLENT DOUBLEGATE LOCATION!   SPACIOUS – 2,500 sq ft of living space - 4 bedrooms – 3.5 baths + Bonus Space!  This home was totally remodeled in 2021/2022!   Offering a great open floor plan, vaulted ceiling, beautiful wood floors, a nice sized kitchen with white cabinets, updated appliances and granite countertops!   The primary suite is located on the main level, has pretty hardwood floors, a private en suite bath with a tiled tub/shower plus a walk-in closet.   Bedroom 2 is also located on the main level with a private bath!   The laundry and a half bath are located downstairs!    Upstairs you will find TWO bedrooms that share a jack/jill bath along with an open bonus room space!   Large fenced backyard!  UPDATES include a new ROOF (2021), updated HVAC units, paint, flooring, lighting, fixtures, countertops, etc!   This home offers space for everyone!
